data.text:
Stretford Paddock is an unofficial Manchester United football club supporter channel. Follow our other social pages to get the full coverage. We do the latest Man Utd news every morning on YouTube and Facebook, we are live on YouTube and Twitter with the team news before every game, there's 4-5 podcasts every week and we're posting 3-4 videos per day on our YouTube channel! Covering every aspect of the club, from academy, history, to the first team be it Premier League, Europa or Champions League, the FA Cup - we are there. This is the audio version!Â Formerly known as Full Time Devils - this is the new era! Subscribe to us on YouTube: http://bit.ly/DEVILSsub
